high_descs: Turn right and exit the room, and take the first right, going straight towards the wall with a doorway on each side, enter the door on the right and go towards the bed.
Pick up the mug from the bed.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn left and go straight, then turn right into the kitchen area towards the sink.
Rinse the mug in the sink.
Look to the countertop to the left of the sink.
Place the mug down on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Wash a Mug and place it on a CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn right to head out of the room and walk down the passage on the right to reach the bedroom on the right to face the bed.
Pick up the mug from the bed.
Head out of the room on the right and walk left to reach the kitchen on the right and face the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink and take it out.
Turn to reach the counter top.
Put the mug on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed mug on the counter top.
